description: Introducing one of a kind 2+ bedroom bi-level condo with 2 full baths on the desirable East Side of South Boston, steps from the beach! This immaculately maintained residence boasts high ceilings, HW floors, central AC, back deck and in unit W/D. While the unit awaits some cosmetic updates, it presents an exciting opportunity to personalize and transform it into your dream home. The spacious layout allows for potential versatility, with the possibility of using the lower level as a 3rd bedroom with en-suite bath. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your own, combining the allure of South Boston living with the potential for customization. Open house Sat & Sun 12-1:30pm.
